### 2. л§Өм№ӯ кҙҖл Ё мЈјмҡ” нҢҢмқј кІҪлЎң (кё°лҢҖ кө¬мЎ°)

#### 2.1 Entity кі„мёө
```
domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/call/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ CallEntity              # нҶөнҷ” кё°лЎқ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ MatchingEntity          # л§Өм№ӯ м •ліҙ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ MatchingPreferenceEntity # л§Өм№ӯ м„ нҳёлҸ„
в””в”Җв”Җ CallStatusEntity        # нҶөнҷ” мғҒнғң мҪ”л“ң
```

**мҳҲмғҒ Entity кө¬мЎ°**:
```kotlin
// CallEntity - нҶөнҷ” кё°лЎқ
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "maum", name = "call")
class CallEntity(
    @Id @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    val id: String,

    val initiatorUserId: String,    // мӢңмһ‘мһҗ
    val receiverUserId: String,     // мҲҳмӢ мһҗ
    val matchingId: String,         // л§Өм№ӯ ID
    val duration: Int,              // нҶөнҷ” мӢңк°„ (мҙҲ)
    val status: Int,                // 0: м—°кІ°мӨ‘, 1: мў…лЈҢ, 2: мӢӨнҢЁ
    val startedAt: LocalDateTime,
    val endedAt: LocalDateTime?,

    @CreatedDate var createdAt: LocalDateTime,
    @LastModifiedDate var updatedAt: LocalDateTime,
)

// MatchingEntity - л§Өм№ӯ м •ліҙ
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "maum", name = "matching")
class MatchingEntity(
    @Id @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    val id: String,

    val userId1: String,            // мӮ¬мҡ©мһҗ1
    val userId2: String,            // мӮ¬мҡ©мһҗ2
    val status: Int,                // 0: лҢҖкё°, 1: л§Өм№ӯлҗЁ, 2: кұ°м Ҳ, 3: м·ЁмҶҢ
    val matchedAt: LocalDateTime?,
    val expireAt: LocalDateTime,    // л§Өм№ӯ л§ҢлЈҢ мӢңк°„

    @CreatedDate var createdAt: LocalDateTime,
    @LastModifiedDate var updatedAt: LocalDateTime,
)

// MatchingQueueEntity - л§Өм№ӯ лҢҖкё° нҒҗ
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "maum", name = "matching_queue")
class MatchingQueueEntity(
    @Id @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    val id: String,

    val userId: String,
    val queuedAt: LocalDateTime,
    val preferences: String,        // JSON: м„ нҳёлҸ„ мЎ°кұҙ
    val status: Int,                // 0: лҢҖкё°, 1: л§Өм№ӯлҗЁ, 2: м·ЁмҶҢ

    @CreatedDate var createdAt: LocalDateTime,
)
```

#### 2.2 Repository кі„мёө
```
domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/call/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ CallRepository
в”ңв”Җв”Җ MatchingRepository
в”ңв”Җв”Җ MatchingQueueRepository
в””в”Җв”Җ MatchingPreferenceRepository
```

**мҳҲмғҒ Repository мқён„°нҺҳмқҙмҠӨ**:
```kotlin
interface MatchingRepository : JpaRepository<MatchingEntity, String> {
    fun findByUserId1(userId: String): List<MatchingEntity>
    fun findByUserId2(userId: String): List<MatchingEntity>
    fun findByUserIdAndStatus(userId: String, status: Int): List<MatchingEntity>
    fun findPendingMatching(userId1: String, userId2: String): MatchingEntity?
    fun findExpiredMatching(now: LocalDateTime): List<MatchingEntity>
}

interface MatchingQueueRepository : JpaRepository<MatchingQueueEntity, String> {
    fun findByUserIdAndStatus(userId: String, status: Int): MatchingQueueEntity?
    fun findPendingQueue(): List<MatchingQueueEntity>
    fun findQueuedBefore(time: LocalDateTime): List<MatchingQueueEntity>
}

interface CallRepository : JpaRepository<CallEntity, String> {
    fun findByInitiatorUserIdOrReceiverUserId(initiatorId: String, receiverId: String): List<CallEntity>
    fun findByMatchingId(matchingId: String): List<CallEntity>
    fun findRecentCalls(userId: String, limit: Int): List<CallEntity>
}
```

---

### 3. нҶөнҷ” кҙҖл Ё мЈјмҡ” нҢҢмқј кІҪлЎң

#### 3.1 Proto м •мқҳ (gRPC мқён„°нҺҳмқҙмҠӨ)
```
protobuf/src/main/proto/call/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ call.proto          # нҶөнҷ” м„ңл№„мҠӨ м •мқҳ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ matching.proto      # л§Өм№ӯ м„ңл№„мҠӨ м •мқҳ
в””в”Җв”Җ call_models.proto   # кіөнҶө лӘЁлҚё
```

**мҳҲмғҒ Proto кө¬мЎ°**:
```protobuf
syntax = "proto3";
package call;

option java_multiple_files = true;
option java_package = "com.maum.backend.protobuf.call";

service CallService {
    rpc StartCall(StartCallRequest) returns (StartCallResponse);
    rpc EndCall(EndCallRequest) returns (EndCallResponse);
    rpc GetCallHistory(GetCallHistoryRequest) returns (GetCallHistoryResponse);
}

service MatchingService {
    rpc EnqueueMatching(EnqueueMatchingRequest) returns (EnqueueMatchingResponse);
    rpc FindMatching(FindMatchingRequest) returns (FindMatchingResponse);
    rpc AcceptMatching(AcceptMatchingRequest) returns (AcceptMatchingResponse);
    rpc RejectMatching(RejectMatchingRequest) returns (RejectMatchingResponse);
    rpc GetMatchingStatus(GetMatchingStatusRequest) returns (GetMatchingStatusResponse);
}

message StartCallRequest {
    string matching_id = 1;
    string initiator_user_id = 2;
    string receiver_user_id = 3;
}

message StartCallResponse {
    string call_id = 1;
    string status = 2;
    int64 expires_at = 3;
}

message EnqueueMatchingRequest {
    string user_id = 1;
    MatchingPreference preference = 2;
}

message FindMatchingRequest {
    string user_id = 1;
}

message FindMatchingResponse {
    string matching_id = 1;
    string matched_user_id = 2;
    int64 expires_at = 3;
}
```

#### 3.2 Service кі„мёө (л№„мҰҲлӢҲмҠӨ лЎңм§Ғ)
```
{call-module}/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/service/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ CallService           # нҶөнҷ” л№„мҰҲлӢҲмҠӨ лЎңм§Ғ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ MatchingService       # л§Өм№ӯ м•Ңкі лҰ¬мҰҳ & лЎңм§Ғ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ MatchingQueueService  # л§Өм№ӯ нҒҗ кҙҖлҰ¬
в””в”Җв”Җ CallHistoryService    # нҶөнҷ” кё°лЎқ кҙҖлҰ¬
```

**мҳҲмғҒ Service кө¬мЎ°**:
```kotlin
@Service
class MatchingService(
    private val matchingRepository: MatchingRepository,
    private val matchingQueueRepository: MatchingQueueRepository,
    private val userService: UserService,
    private val applicationEventPublisher: ApplicationEventPublisher,
) {

    @Transactional
    fun enqueueMatching(userId: String, preferences: MatchingPreference): MatchingQueueEntity {
        // 1. кё°мЎҙ нҒҗ нҷ•мқё
        val existing = matchingQueueRepository.findByUserIdAndStatus(userId, WAITING)
        if (existing != null) throw AlreadyInQueueException()

        // 2. мғҲ нҒҗ н•ӯлӘ© мғқм„ұ
        val queueEntity = MatchingQueueEntity(
            userId = userId,
            preferences = preferences.toJson(),
            status = WAITING,
        )
        return matchingQueueRepository.save(queueEntity)
    }

    @Transactional
    fun findMatching(userId: String): MatchingEntity? {
        // 1. нҒҗм—җм„ң лҢҖкё° мӨ‘мқё мӮ¬мҡ©мһҗ м°ҫкё°
        val queue = matchingQueueRepository.findByUserIdAndStatus(userId, WAITING)
            ?: throw NotInQueueException()

        // 2. л§Өм№ӯ м•Ңкі лҰ¬мҰҳ: м„ нҳёлҸ„м—җ л§һлҠ” лҢҖмғҒ м°ҫкё°
        val candidates = findCandidates(userId, queue.preferences)
        val matchedUser = selectBestMatch(candidates)
            ?: return null  // л§Өм№ӯ лҢҖмғҒ м—ҶмқҢ

        // 3. л§Өм№ӯ мғқм„ұ
        val matching = MatchingEntity(
            userId1 = userId,
            userId2 = matchedUser.id,
            status = MATCHED,
            matchedAt = LocalDateTime.now(),
            expireAt = LocalDateTime.now().plusMinutes(2), // 2л¶„ нғҖмһ„м•„мӣғ
        )
        val saved = matchingRepository.save(matching)

        // 4. мғҒлҢҖл°© нҒҗм—җм„ң м ңкұ°
        matchingQueueRepository.deleteById(matchedUser.queueId!!)

        // 5. мқҙлІӨнҠё л°ңн–ү
        applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(
            MatchingCompleteEvent(saved.id, userId, matchedUser.id)
        )

        return saved
    }

    private fun findCandidates(userId: String, preferences: MatchingPreference): List<UserInfo> {
        val pendingQueues = matchingQueueRepository.findPendingQueue()
        return pendingQueues
            .filter { it.userId != userId }
            .filter { meetsPreferences(it, preferences) }
            .sortByDescending { calculateMatchScore(userId, it.userId) }
    }

    @Transactional
    fun acceptMatching(matchingId: String): MatchingEntity {
        val matching = matchingRepository.findById(matchingId)
            .orElseThrow { MatchingNotFoundException() }

        if (matching.status != PENDING_ACCEPT) {
            throw InvalidMatchingStatusException()
        }

        matching.status = ACCEPTED
        matching.acceptedAt = LocalDateTime.now()

        applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(
            MatchingAcceptedEvent(matchingId)
        )

        return matchingRepository.save(matching)
    }

    @Scheduled(fixedDelay = 60000) // 1л¶„л§ҲлӢӨ мӢӨн–ү
    @Transactional
    fun cleanupExpiredMatching() {
        val now = LocalDateTime.now()
        val expiredMatching = matchingRepository.findExpiredMatching(now)

        expiredMatching.forEach {
            it.status = EXPIRED
            matchingRepository.save(it)

            applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(
                MatchingExpiredEvent(it.id, it.userId1, it.userId2)
            )
        }
    }
}

@Service
class CallService(
    private val callRepository: CallRepository,
    private val matchingRepository: MatchingRepository,
    private val applicationEventPublisher: ApplicationEventPublisher,
) {

    @Transactional
    fun startCall(matchingId: String, initiatorId: String): CallEntity {
        // 1. л§Өм№ӯ кІҖмҰқ
        val matching = matchingRepository.findById(matchingId)
            .orElseThrow { MatchingNotFoundException() }

        if (matching.status != ACCEPTED) {
            throw InvalidMatchingStatusException()
        }

        // 2. нҶөнҷ” кё°лЎқ мғқм„ұ
        val call = CallEntity(
            matchingId = matchingId,
            initiatorUserId = initiatorId,
            receiverUserId = getReceiverUserId(matching, initiatorId),
            status = CALLING,
            startedAt = LocalDateTime.now(),
        )
        val savedCall = callRepository.save(call)

        // 3. мқҙлІӨнҠё л°ңн–ү (WebSocket м•ҢлҰј)
        applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(
            CallInitiatedEvent(savedCall.id, initiatorId, savedCall.receiverUserId)
        )

        return savedCall
    }

    @Transactional
    fun endCall(callId: String, duration: Int): CallEntity {
        val call = callRepository.findById(callId)
            .orElseThrow { CallNotFoundException() }

        call.status = COMPLETED
        call.duration = duration
        call.endedAt = LocalDateTime.now()

        val saved = callRepository.save(call)

        // нҶөнҷ” мў…лЈҢ мқҙлІӨнҠё
        applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(
            CallEndedEvent(callId, call.initiatorUserId, call.receiverUserId, duration)
        )

        return saved
    }
}
```

#### 3.3 gRPC Controller (м„ңлІ„)
```
{call-module}/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/controller/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ CallGrpcService
в””в”Җв”Җ MatchingGrpcService
```

**мҳҲмғҒ кө¬нҳ„**:
```kotlin
@GrpcService
class MatchingGrpcService(
    private val matchingService: MatchingService,
) : MatchingServiceGrpc.MatchingServiceImplBase() {

    override fun findMatching(
        request: FindMatchingRequest,
        responseObserver: StreamObserver<FindMatchingResponse>,
    ) {
        try {
            val matching = matchingService.findMatching(request.userId)
            if (matching != null) {
                val response = FindMatchingResponse.newBuilder()
                    .setMatchingId(matching.id)
                    .setMatchedUserId(
                        if (matching.userId1 == request.userId) matching.userId2
                        else matching.userId1
                    )
                    .setExpiresAt(matching.expireAt.time)
                    .build()
                responseObserver.onNext(response)
            }
            responseObserver.onCompleted()
        } catch (e: Exception) {
            responseObserver.onError(
                Status.INTERNAL
                    .withDescription(e.message)
                    .asRuntimeException()
            )
        }
    }

    override fun acceptMatching(
        request: AcceptMatchingRequest,
        responseObserver: StreamObserver<AcceptMatchingResponse>,
    ) {
        try {
            val matching = matchingService.acceptMatching(request.matchingId)
            val response = AcceptMatchingResponse.newBuilder()
                .setStatus("ACCEPTED")
                .build()
            responseObserver.onNext(response)
            responseObserver.onCompleted()
        } catch (e: Exception) {
            responseObserver.onError(
                Status.INVALID_ARGUMENT
                    .withDescription(e.message)
                    .asRuntimeException()
            )
        }
    }
}
```

#### 3.4 GraphQL кі„мёө
```
graphql/src/main/resources/graphql/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ call.graphqls        # нҶөнҷ” кҙҖл Ё GraphQL мҠӨнӮӨл§Ҳ
в””в”Җв”Җ matching.graphqls    # л§Өм№ӯ кҙҖл Ё GraphQL мҠӨнӮӨл§Ҳ

graphql/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ service/call/        # gRPC нҒҙлқјмқҙм–ёнҠё
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ CallService
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ MatchingService
в””в”Җв”Җ controller/call/     # GraphQL лҰ¬мЎёлІ„
    в”ңв”Җв”Җ CallController
    в””в”Җв”Җ MatchingController
```

**мҳҲмғҒ GraphQL мҠӨнӮӨл§Ҳ**:
```graphql
# matching.graphqls
type Matching {
    id: ID!
    userId1: String!
    userId2: String!
    status: String!        # WAITING, MATCHED, ACCEPTED, EXPIRED, REJECTED
    matchedAt: String
    expiresAt: String!
    createdAt: String!
}

type MatchingQueue {
    id: ID!
    status: String!
    position: Int          # лҢҖкё°м—ҙ мҲңм„ң
}

input MatchingPreferenceInput {
    ageMin: Int
    ageMax: Int
    genderPreference: String  # M, F, ANY
    regionPreference: String
}

extend type Query {
    matching(matchingId: ID!): Matching
    myMatching: Matching                              # нҳ„мһ¬ л§Өм№ӯ
    myMatchingQueue: MatchingQueue                    # лӮҙ лҢҖкё°м—ҙ мғҒнғң
}

extend type Mutation {
    enqueueMatching(preferences: MatchingPreferenceInput!): MatchingQueue!
    dequeueMatching: Boolean!
    acceptMatching(matchingId: ID!): Matching!
    rejectMatching(matchingId: ID!): Matching!
}
```

